Trevor McFedries (amụrụ na Nọvemba 27, 1985), bụ ónyé nchoputa na onye isi oche nke teknụzụ mmalite Brud na ónyé okike nke kpakpando pop Miquela ma ọ bụ Lil Miquela
Ọrụ McFedries na Brud na-elekwasị anya n'iji teknụzụ na-agbanye ókèala iji wuo ụlọ ọrụ ntụrụndụ siri ike, nke nwéré ọgụgụ isi, na nke dị mfe màkà ọgbọ ọhụrụ

Tupu o mepụta Brud, a maara ya dịka Yung Skeeter ma rụọ ọrụ dị ka DJ, onye na-emepụta ihe, na ónyé nduzi màkà ihe omume gụnyere Ke$ha, Azealia Banks, Katy Perry, Chris Brown, Steve Aoki, na ndị ọzọ. Ọ gàrà njem n'akụkụ Katy Perry na 2011 California Dreams Tour. McFedries emeela emume egwu Lollapalooza na Coachella, jere ozi dị ka onye ọchụnta ego bi na Bad Robot, ma bụrụkwa ónyé ọrụ mbụ na Spotify.

McFedries tolitere na Davenport, Iowa. N'ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị, ọ bụ "onye na-agba bọọlụ" ma nwee mmasị igwu bọọlụ. Ya na ezinụlọ ya kwagara Los Angeles mgbè ọ dị afọ iri na isii. Ọ nwetara agụmakwụkwọ kọleji iji gbaa bọọlụ na San Jose State mana ọ hapụrụ kọleji wee laghachi LA. Los Angeles abụwo "ụlọ" ya kemgbe oge ahụ
Ọ malitere DJing mgbè ọ dị afọ 19.
McFedries weere aha egwu DJ Skeet Skeet, na 2007 a kọwaara ya Shwayze na Cisco Adler. Ha atọ mepụtara mmekọrịta nke ga-ejedebe na ntọhapụ nke 2008 nke abọm akpọrọ onwe ya

Abọm ahụ mèrè ya n'elu 10 na chaatị Billboard na egwu abụọ ("Buzzin'" na "Corona na Lime") nke gosipụtara na ndepụta Billboard Hot 100. Ịbụ onye a ma ama nke mmadụ atọ ahụ dugara n'ịmepụta usoro ihe nkiri telivishọn dị mkpirikpi na MTV a na-akpọ Buzzin. Ọzọkwa na 2008, e nyere DJ Skeet Skeet "People's Choice Award for Best DJ" site na Paper Magazine. Ọ ghọkwara ónyé DJ mbụ na-eme ihe ngosi niile na Warped Tour na 2008.
